userTemplate:
Language: {{lang}}
Title: {{title}}
Description: {{description}}
Goal: {{goal}}

Tasks:
1) Rewrite description to be clear, step-by-step, and easy to prove.
2) Suggest a simple reward/points idea.
3) Create a viral tweet pack (zh/en + 3-6 hashtags + cta).

Return ONLY JSON:
{
  "optimizedDescription": "...",
  "rewardSuggestion": "...",
  "viralTweet": {"tweet_zh":"...","tweet_en":"...","hashtags":["#WAOC"],"cta":"..."}
}
If lang is "zh", optimizedDescription and rewardSuggestion should be in Chinese. viralTweet should still include both zh/en.
